---

<Layout
  title="AI Training for Youth 17-24 | Get Hired in 8 Weeks | Upstate SC"
  description="Launch your AI career in 8 weeks with hands-on training, 3 portfolio projects, and job placement support. Starting $45K-$65K. Free for WIOA-eligible youth. No experience needed."
  ogImage="/images/ai-training-hero.jpg"
  ogImageAlt="AI Training for Youth - Professional AI Certification South Carolina"
  noindex={true}
  twitterTitle="Launch Your AI Career Before You're 25 | AI Training for Youth"
  twitterDescription="8 weeks. 3 portfolio projects. 1 certification. Your AI career launches here. Ages 17-24. Free for WIOA-eligible youth."
  geoRegion="US-SC"
  geoPlacename="South Carolina"
  geoPosition="34.0007;-81.0348"
  keywords="AI training for youth, AI career launch, youth AI certification SC, entry level AI jobs, youth workforce development, WIOA training, career transition youth"
  structuredData={structuredData}
>
  <!-- Modal Manager -->
  <AITrainingModalManager client:load />

  <main>
    <!-- HERO SECTION -->
    <section class="ai-training-hero min-h-[600px] md:min-h-[700px] flex items-center justify-center relative text-primary-foreground">
      <!-- Background Image -->
      <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-cover bg-center bg-no-repeat hero-bg-image"></div>

      <!-- Glassy Overlay -->
      <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-br from-primary/55 to-primary/50 backdrop-blur-[2px]"></div>

      <div class="mx-auto px-4 py-24 relative z-10 hero-content-wrapper">
        <div class="w-full text-center">

          <!-- Logo -->
          <div class="mb-8">
            <img
              src="/images/logo/2x/ai-training-course-white-logo@2x.png"
              alt="AI Training Course"
              class="h-16 w-auto mx-auto"
              loading="eager"
            >
          </div>

          <!-- Badge -->
          <div class="badge-text inline-flex items-center gap-2 bg-white/20 backdrop-blur rounded-full px-4 py-2 mb-6">
            <span class="text-white font-semibold uppercase badge-text">For Ages 17-24</span>
          </div>

          <!-- Main Headline - YOUTH FOCUSED -->
          <h1 class="text-3xl md:text-5xl font-bold mb-6 leading-tight">
            Launch Your AI Career Before You're 25
          </h1>

          <!-- Subheadline - YOUTH FOCUSED -->
          <p class="text-lg md:text-xl mb-8 leading-relaxed">
            You're 17-24. AI is transforming every industry. In 8 weeks, you'll be certified with a professional portfolio that proves your skills to employers. No coding experience required. Start earning $45K-$65K in your first AI role.
          </p>

          <!-- Call to Action Button -->
          <AITrainingButton client:load />

        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- URGENCY SECTION -->
    <section class="ai-training-urgency py-8 bg-accent">
      <div class="container mx-auto px-4">
        <div class="text-center">
          <p class="text-xl md:text-2xl font-bold text-white">
            Only 15 spots for first cohort starting January 15 — Next cohort: March
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- THE CHALLENGE SECTION - YOUTH REPOSITIONED -->
    <section class="ai-training-problem py-24 bg-muted/30">
      <div class="container mx-auto px-4">
        <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
          <div class="text-center mb-12">
            <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold mb-6 text-primary">
              The Challenge You're Facing
            </h2>
            <p class="text-lg text-muted-foreground">
              You're 17-24. You're watching peers figure out careers. You know AI is important. But you're stuck.
            </p>
          </div>

          <div class="space-y-6 mb-12">
            <!-- Option 1: College -->
            <Card>
              <CardContent className="p-8">
                <div class="flex items-start gap-4">
                  <div class="text-3xl font-bold text-destructive flex-shrink-0">✕</div>
                  <div>
                    <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-2 text-foreground">4-Year Computer Science Degree</h3>
                    <p class="text-muted-foreground">Takes 4 years. Costs $60K-$100K. By the time you graduate, AI will have evolved twice. And you still won't have real projects employers want to see.</p>
                  </div>
                </div>
              </CardContent>
            </Card>

            <!-- Option 2: Bootcamp -->
            <Card>
              <CardContent className="p-8">
                <div class="flex items-start gap-4">
                  <div class="text-3xl font-bold text-destructive flex-shrink-0">✕</div>
                  <div>
                    <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-2 text-foreground">Expensive Bootcamp ($10K-$20K, 12-24 weeks)</h3>
                    <p class="text-muted-foreground">Long. Expensive. Leaves you with theory, not professional portfolio projects that prove you can actually do the work.</p>
                  </div>
                </div>
              </CardContent>
            </Card>

            <!-- Option 3: Online courses -->
            <Card>
              <CardContent className="p-8">
                <div class="flex items-start gap-4">
                  <div class="text-3xl font-bold text-destructive flex-shrink-0">✕</div>
                  <div>
                    <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-2 text-foreground">Online Courses (Coursera, Udemy)</h3>
                    <p class="text-muted-foreground">Self-paced sounds good until you realize... you stop. No accountability. No community. No one pushing you to actually finish.</p>
                  </div>
                </div>
              </CardContent>
            </Card>
          </div>

          <!-- Meanwhile -->
          <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl shadow-lg p-8 md:p-12 border-2 border-accent">
            <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-6 text-primary text-center">Meanwhile...</h3>
            <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-6">
              <div class="flex items-start gap-3">
                <div class="text-2xl">✓</div>
                <div>
                  <p class="font-semibold text-foreground">AI jobs are growing 25% annually</p>
                </div>
              </div>
              <div class="flex items-start gap-3">
                <div class="text-2xl">✓</div>
                <div>
                  <p class="font-semibold text-foreground">Entry-level roles start at $45K-$65K</p>
                </div>
              </div>
              <div class="flex items-start gap-3">
                <div class="text-2xl">✓</div>
                <div>
                  <p class="font-semibold text-foreground">Companies are hiring NOW</p>
                </div>
              </div>
              <div class="flex items-start gap-3">
                <div class="text-2xl">✓</div>
                <div>
                  <p class="font-semibold text-foreground">Other people your age are getting certified this month</p>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>

          <p class="text-xl text-foreground font-semibold mt-12 text-center">
            You don't have 4 years. You don't have $20K. You need a real path that works for your life right now.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- THE SOLUTION SECTION -->
    <section class="three-step-process-new py-24 bg-gray-50">
      <div class="container mx-auto px-4">
        <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto">
          <div class="text-center mb-16">
            <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold mb-6 text-primary">
              Your 8-Week Path to AI Career Launch
            </h2>
            <p class="text-xl text-muted-foreground max-w-3xl mx-auto font-semibold">
              Build real portfolio projects. Get certified. Get hired.
            </p>
          </div>

          <!-- Three Tiers -->
          <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-8 mb-20">
            <!-- Tier 1: Foundation -->
            <div class="text-center">
              <div class="relative mb-8">
                <div class="w-48 h-48 mx-auto bg-gradient-to-br from-primary to-primary/90 step-square flex flex-col items-center justify-center shadow-xl">
                  <span class="step-number font-black text-white drop-shadow-lg text-4xl">WEEKS</span>
                  <span class="step-number font-black text-[#F66733] drop-shadow-lg text-3xl">1-4</span>
                </div>
              </div>
              <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-4 text-primary">Foundation</h3>
              <p class="text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">
                Learn AI fundamentals, machine learning, computer vision, NLP, and generative AI. Hands-on with real tools. No theory without practice.
              </p>
            </div>

            <!-- Tier 2: Portfolio -->
            <div class="text-center">
              <div class="relative mb-8">
                <div class="w-48 h-48 mx-auto bg-gradient-to-br from-accent to-accent/90 step-square flex flex-col items-center justify-center shadow-xl">
                  <span class="step-number step-wk font-black text-white drop-shadow-lg text-4xl">WEEKS</span>
                  <span class="step-number s font-black text-[#3D4E76] drop-shadow-lg text-3xl">5-7</span>
                </div>
              </div>
              <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-4 text-primary">Portfolio Projects</h3>
              <p class="text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">
                Build 3 professional portfolio projects. These are the artifacts employers actually want to see. Real problems. Real solutions. Real proof.
              </p>
            </div>

            <!-- Tier 3: Launch -->
            <div class="text-center">
              <div class="relative mb-8">
                <div class="w-48 h-48 mx-auto bg-gradient-to-br from-primary to-primary/90 step-square flex flex-col items-center justify-center shadow-xl">
                  <span class="step-number font-black text-white drop-shadow-lg text-4xl">WEEK</span>
                  <span class="step-number font-black text-[#F66733] drop-shadow-lg text-3xl">8</span>
                </div>
              </div>
              <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-4 text-primary">Career Launch</h3>
              <p class="text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">
                Get certified. Optimize resume + LinkedIn. Interview prep. Launch job search with confidence and support.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>

          <!-- What You'll Learn -->
          <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl shadow-xl p-8 md:p-12">
            <div class="text-center mb-8">
              <h3 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold mb-6 text-primary">
                What's Included:
              </h3>
            </div>

            <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-6 mb-8">
              <div class="flex items-start gap-3 p-4 bg-green-50 rounded-lg">
                <div class="w-2 h-2 bg-green-500 rounded-full flex-shrink-0 mt-2"></div>
                <span class="text-gray-700 font-medium">Live in-person instruction (6 hours/week)</span>
              </div>
              <div class="flex items-start gap-3 p-4 bg-green-50 rounded-lg">
                <div class="w-2 h-2 bg-green-500 rounded-full flex-shrink-0 mt-2"></div>
                <span class="text-gray-700 font-medium">3 professional portfolio projects</span>
              </div>
              <div class="flex items-start gap-3 p-4 bg-green-50 rounded-lg">
                <div class="w-2 h-2 bg-green-500 rounded-full flex-shrink-0 mt-2"></div>
                <span class="text-gray-700 font-medium">Industry-recognized AI certification</span>
              </div>
              <div class="flex items-start gap-3 p-4 bg-green-50 rounded-lg">
                <div class="w-2 h-2 bg-green-500 rounded-full flex-shrink-0 mt-2"></div>
                <span class="text-gray-700 font-medium">Career coaching + job search support</span>
              </div>
              <div class="flex items-start gap-3 p-4 bg-green-50 rounded-lg">
                <div class="w-2 h-2 bg-green-500 rounded-full flex-shrink-0 mt-2"></div>
                <span class="text-gray-700 font-medium">Resume + LinkedIn optimization</span>
              </div>
              <div class="flex items-start gap-3 p-4 bg-green-50 rounded-lg">
                <div class="w-2 h-2 bg-green-500 rounded-full flex-shrink-0 mt-2"></div>
                <span class="text-gray-700 font-medium">Interview prep and mock interviews</span>
              </div>
            </div>

            <!-- Pricing Section (Russell's Youth Funnel: 100% FREE focus) -->
            <div class="mb-8">
              <!-- Primary: FREE for WIOA-Eligible -->
              <div class="p-8 bg-gradient-to-br from-green-50 to-green-100 rounded-lg border-2 border-green-300">
                <div class="text-center">
                  <h4 class="text-xl font-bold text-primary mb-3">WIOA-Eligible Youth</h4>
                  <p class="text-6xl font-bold text-green-600 mb-3">FREE</p>
                  <p class="text-gray-700 leading-relaxed">
                    SC Works covers your full tuition. Check eligibility with your local SC Works office. Most youth 17-24 qualify if you're displaced, low-income, or underemployed.
                  </p>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>

            <!-- Limited Availability Notice -->
            <div class="text-center p-6 bg-accent/10 rounded-lg border-2 border-accent/30">
              <p class="text-lg font-semibold text-primary mb-2">Only 15 Spots for First Cohort</p>
              <p class="text-gray-700">Cohort starts January 15. Next cohort starts March. Spots fill fast.</p>
            </div>

            <!-- CTA Button -->
            <div class="text-center mt-8">
              <AITrainingButton client:load />
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- COMPARISON CHART: TRAINING OPTIONS -->
    <section class="py-24 bg-gradient-to-br from-gray-50 to-blue-50">
      <div class="container mx-auto px-4">
        <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto">
          <div class="text-center mb-16">
            <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold mb-6 text-primary">
              Your Options: How We Compare
            </h2>
            <p class="text-lg text-muted-foreground max-w-2xl mx-auto">
              See why 8 weeks of intensive training beats 4 years, $20K, or self-study
            </p>
          </div>

          <div class="overflow-x-auto">
            <table class="w-full text-sm border-collapse">
              <thead>
                <tr class="bg-primary text-white">
                  <th class="border border-gray-300 px-4 py-3 text-left">Factor</th>
                  <th class="border border-gray-300 px-4 py-3 text-center bg-accent font-bold">AI Fundamentals (8 weeks)</th>
                  <th class="border border-gray-300 px-4 py-3 text-center">4-Year Degree</th>
                  <th class="border border-gray-300 px-4 py-3 text-center">Expensive Bootcamp</th>
                  <th class="border border-gray-300 px-4 py-3 text-center">Self-Study Online</th>
                </tr>
              </thead>
              <tbody>
                <tr class="hover:bg-white/50 transition">
                  <td class="border border-gray-300 px-4 py-3 font-bold text-gray-900">Time Investment</td>
                  <td class="border border-gray-300 px-4 py-3 text-center bg-green-50"><span class="font-bold text-green-700">8 weeks</span></td>
                  <td class="border border-gray-300 px-4 py-3 text-center text-red-600 font-bold">4 years</td>
                  <td class="border border-gray-300 px-4 py-3 text-center text-red-600 font-bold">12-24 weeks</td>
                  <td class="border border-gray-300 px-4 py-3 text-center">Indefinite</td>
                </tr>
                <tr class="hover:bg-white/50 transition">
                  <td class="border border-gray-300 px-4 py-3 font-bold text-gray-900">Cost</td>
                  <td class="border border-gray-300 px-4 py-3 text-center bg-green-50"><span class="font-bold text-green-700">FREE</span></td>
                  <td class="border border-gray-300 px-4 py-3 text-center text-red-600 font-bold">$60K-$100K</td>
                  <td class="border border-gray-300 px-4 py-3 text-center text-red-600 font-bold">$10K-$20K</td>
                  <td class="border border-gray-300 px-4 py-3 text-center">$100-$500</td>
                </tr>
                <tr class="hover:bg-white/50 transition">
                  <td class="border border-gray-300 px-4 py-3 font-bold text-gray-900">Portfolio Projects</td>
                  <td class="border border-gray-300 px-4 py-3 text-center bg-green-50"><span class="font-bold text-green-700">3 real projects</span></td>
                  <td class="border border-gray-300 px-4 py-3 text-center">Varies (mostly theory)</td>
                  <td class="border border-gray-300 px-4 py-3 text-center">1-2 projects</td>
                  <td class="border border-gray-300 px-4 py-3 text-center">Self-directed (optional)</td>
                </tr>
                <tr class="hover:bg-white/50 transition">
                  <td class="border border-gray-300 px-4 py-3 font-bold text-gray-900">Instructor Support</td>
                  <td class="border border-gray-300 px-4 py-3 text-center bg-green-50"><span class="font-bold text-green-700">Live, 2x/week</span></td>
                  <td class="border border-gray-300 px-4 py-3 text-center">Large classes, limited</td>
                  <td class="border border-gray-300 px-4 py-3 text-center">Some support</td>
                  <td class="border border-gray-300 px-4 py-3 text-center">Community only</td>
                </tr>
